risk-weight category appropriate to the party that is obligated to reimburse the servicer. 





If the servicer is not entitled to full reimbursement, then the maximum possible amount of any nonreimbursed advances
on any one loan must be contractually limited to an insignificant amount of the outstanding principal on that loan
